# four-layer-architecture — local notes

This file holds per-project preferences for the four-layer-architecture
plugin's teach-back system. Edit the YAML frontmatter above to tune
behaviour; use the body for freeform notes to yourself.

**Location:** copy this template to `.claude/four-layer-architecture.local.md`
in your project root. The file is gitignored so it stays per-user. Do NOT
rename it — the plugin's hook script looks for that exact path.

## What the settings do

* **`teach_back.auto_suggest`** — when `true`, the `PreToolUse` hook prints
  a single advisory line on structural edits (new agent / skill / command /
  `plugin.json` change). Set `false` to mute.

* **`teach_back.first_use_shown`** — flips to `true` once the
  `SessionStart` first-use nudge has fired. Flip back to `false` if you
  want to see it again (e.g. after major project changes).

* **`teach_back.depth`** — default depth for
  `/four-layer-architecture:feynman-check` when invoked without
  `--deep`/`--lite`. One of `lite`, `deep`, or `off`.

* **`teach_back.skip_paths`** — YAML list of glob patterns where the
  structural-edit hook stays silent even when `auto_suggest: true`.
  Example: `["plugins/*/hooks/*"]` silences the nudge on hook-script
  edits while keeping it active for everything else.

* **`journal.max_lines`** — threshold at which the plugin offers to
  archive `.four-layer-journal.md` to a dated file.

* **`socratic.default_topic`** — if set, `/four-layer-architecture:socratic`
  with no argument picks this topic directly instead of showing the
  two-pane menu.

## Alternative skip channels

Two other ways to mute teach-back, independent of this file:

1. **Declared in instructions** — add a line containing
   `four-layer-architecture: skip-teach-back` to your project's `AGENTS.md`
   or `CLAUDE.md`. This opts out for every collaborator (the token is
   checked into git).

2. **In-session bail-out** — during any Feynman or Socratic round, reply
   with `skip`, `enough`, `move on`, `I know this`, `proceed`, or `next`.
   The agent yields immediately. No re-prompt this session.

